[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] An Act for abolishing certain Offices of the High Court of Chancery in England.
[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] An Act to explain and amend certain Enactments contained respectively in the Acts for the Regulation of Municipal Corporations in England and Wales, and in Ireland.
[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] to empower Landed Proprietors in Ireland to sink, embank, and remove Obstructions in Rivers.
[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] An Act for regulating the Carriage of Passengers in Merchant Vessels.
[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] An Act for enabling Ecclesiastical Corporations, aggregate and sole, to grant Leases for long Terms of Years.
[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] An Act for the Appointment and Payment of Parish Constables.
[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] An Act to annex the County of the City of Coventry to Warwickshire, and to define the Boundary of the City of Coventry.
[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] An Act to confirm the Incorporation of certain Boroughs, and to indemnify such Persons as have sustained Loss thereby.
[src:river-severn/5-6-vict-p02] An Act for suspending, until the First Day of October One thousand eight hundred and forty-three, Appointments to certain Ecclesiastical Preferments in the Dioceses of Saint Asaph and Bangor, and for securing certain Property to the said Sees.
